@startuml UC_Agendar_Turno
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor Recepcionista
actor Paciente

package "Agendar Turno" {
  usecase "Agendar Turno" as UC_Agendar
  usecase "Buscar Paciente" as UC_Buscar
  usecase "Seleccionar Profesional" as UC_SelProf
  usecase "Seleccionar Tipo de Consulta" as UC_TipoConsulta
  usecase "Mostrar Disponibilidad" as UC_MostrarDisp
  usecase "Validar Disponibilidad" as UC_Validar
  usecase "Verificar Superposición" as UC_Superposicion
  usecase "Registrar Turno" as UC_Registrar
  usecase "Generar Recordatorio" as UC_Recordatorio
}

Recepcionista --> UC_Agendar
Paciente ..> UC_Agendar : interesado en

UC_Agendar --> UC_Buscar
UC_Agendar --> UC_SelProf
UC_Agendar --> UC_TipoConsulta
UC_Agendar --> UC_MostrarDisp

UC_MostrarDisp .> UC_Validar : <<include>>
UC_MostrarDisp .> UC_Superposicion : <<include>>

UC_MostrarDisp --> UC_Registrar
UC_Registrar .> UC_Recordatorio : <<include>>

UC_TipoConsulta --> UC_MostrarDisp

@enduml